# Cloudflare Pages redirects — Godberry Studios
#
# /go/{slug} — affiliate redirect cloak.
#   Readers click an internal same-origin link, Cloudflare 302s to the vendor.
#   Why: many browser extensions (uBlock, AdGuard filter lists, Brave Shields)
#   hide or strip anchors that point directly to known affiliate URL patterns.
#   Routing through /go/{slug} keeps the hrefs same-origin so extensions don't
#   interfere, while Google still sees rel="sponsored nofollow" on the anchor.
#
# Format: <path>  <destination>  <status>
#   - Use 302 (temporary) so affiliate attribution parameters can be rotated
#     without Google caching a 301.
#   - Keep tracking query params intact in the destination.
#
# Add a new vendor:
#   1. Sign up / get the vendor's referral URL + param.
#   2. Add a line below: /go/<slug>  <full vendor referral URL>  302
#   3. Log in AFFILIATE-PLAYBOOK.md Active Programs table.
#   4. Use {{< affiliate slug="<slug>" label="..." >}} in posts.

/go/make  https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=godberry  302
